data.description: Stop what you are doing and check out this 4 bedroom beauty nestled on 5 acres near Rocky Fork! This well-maintained home built in 2002 features a new furnace and central air unit, large eat in kitchen with newer stainless appliances and modern white cabinetry. The living room offers a spacious open floor plan  with hardwood floors and wood burning stove. Fall in love with the charming entryway and 1/2 bath, climb the stairs to second floor to find 2 full bathrooms, 3 generous bedrooms and laundry conveniently located in the master bath. The full unfinished walkout basement offers endless potential if more living space or storage is needed. The first floor bedroom would make the perfect home office if you work remotely. Need room for your toys? Store them in the 2 car attached garage. Propane tank is filled and ready for cold weather.  If you are ready to hunt, or just enjoy the great outdoors, this home checks all the boxes. Call today to schedule your personal tour!
